action.title: Action
action.description: The fists are furious, the guns are blazing, and the drama is sizzling in these edge-of-your-seat hits.

283943.title: Hunt to Kill
283943.description: A border patrol agent quits and moves to the woods with his daughter, but when she is kidnapped by a band of criminals he steps back into action.

300452.title: The Man In The Iron Mask
300452.description: Three former musketeers attempt to unseat the tyrannical King Louis XIV and replace him with his alleged (and imprisoned) long lost twin.

301235.title: Navy Seals
301235.description: When Middle-Eastern terrorists acquire some American stinger missiles, it's up to the U.S. Navy's elite commando unit, the Navy SEALS, to ward off their challenge and blow them up.

302326.title: Gang Related
302326.description: Two men face the consequences after they kill a man and pin the murder on an innocent transient.

302681.title: The Alamo
302681.description: John Wayne and Richard Widmark star in this historical film spectacular about the attack by Mexican troops on the Alamo.

303076.title: Chato's Land
303076.description: A half-white, half-Apache man dodges a vengeful posse after he kills a sheriff in self-defense. Both sides pay a heavy price in this Western.

304805.title: I'm Gonna Git You Sucka
304805.description: This ultra-hip parody in the tradition of "The Naked Gun" and "Airplane" stars Keenan Ivory Wayans in an action-adventure filled with screwball gags and side-splitting one-liners.

306929.title: The Devil's Brigade
306929.description: In this true WWII story, an American colonel creates the First Special Service Force from a group of misfits. A dangerous mission soon awaits.

306946.title: Run Silent, Run Deep
306946.description: With sweat-dripping realism, this taut drama stars Clark Gable as a single-minded sub commander who must contend with a tough executive officer (Burt Lancaster) and attacks from enemy forces.

307753.title: Kickboxer
307753.description: After a kickboxing champ is paralyzed fighting Thailand’s top fighter, his brother vows vengeance but must learn Muay Thai to fight back.

367706.title: Jailbait
367706.description: She killed her stepfather in self-defense. Now, Anna must fight her dark side and survive the world of girl gangs and predatory guards in juvy.

367819.title: Titanic 2
367819.description: A century after the fateful voyage of the original, modern luxury liner Titanic II sets sail. Will this ship suffer the same fate as her namesake?

389503.title: Robocop
389503.description: A cop who died in the line of duty is transformed into a chrome-plated cyborg policeman with an indestructible new body and a thirst for revenge.

389506.title: Robocop 2
389506.description: In a dystopian Detroit, drug dealers run rampant. Cyborg cop Alex Murphy returns to take on both a crime boss and a twisted version of his own self.

401472.title: Colors
401472.description: A veteran cop and his new partner are called in to assist with the crackdown against mounting gang violence in the slums of East Los Angeles.

438052.title: Centurion
438052.description: Quintus Dias, the sole survivor of a Pictish raid, marches with General Virilus' Ninth Legion, with orders to destroy the Picts and kill their leader.

448434.title: Bait
448434.description: When a freak tsunami traps people inside a supermarket, a pack of killer sharks let them know they aren’t the only ones who are shopping for dinner.

463206.title: El Pistolero
463206.description: Un poderoso llega a un pueblo en busca de nuevos pistoleros para su equipo y un hombre sencillo acepta el trabajo para vengar la muerte de su padre.

465295.title: Guardians (English Dub)
465295.description: Formed during the Cold War, an elite squad of superheroes return to action when new threats arise that threaten the safety of the world.

465367.title: Bones
465367.description: 20 years after his death, a local legend and benefactor returns as a ghost to avenge those who killed him and restore his neighborhood.

465428.title: Gods of Egypt
465428.description: A mortal tries to save the world and his own true love by joining with a powerful god in an epic battle against his rival, the deadly god of darkness.

469130.title: Code Name: The Cleaner
469130.description: With no memory of his past, and everyone out to get him, an average guy's only hope of survival is to become the world's worst superspy.

469586.title: Hard Target
469586.description: The line between the hunted and the hunter becomes blurred when one man finds himself fighting a group that hunts other men for blood sport.

475643.title: Stargate
475643.description: A historical expert and a military unit travel through a mysterious portal. They land in a bizarre world occupied by a dangerous and powerful being.

476644.title: The Boondock Saints
476644.description: Irish brothers try to clean up Boston’s underworld by knocking off gangsters and become local folk heroes, as an FBI agent traces their bloody trail.

477962.title: Set It Off
477962.description: Four African-American women in Los Angeles, all in dire financial circumstances, resort to robbing banks with action-packed, tragic consequences.

486566.title: Over the Top
486566.description: A truck driver attempts to reconnect with his estranged son as he road trips to Las Vegas to compete in an arm wrestling championship.

494842.title: Shottas
494842.description: Two young men from Jamaica climb to the top of the criminal world in Miami, with a constant presence of drugs, extortion, and deceit.

497642.title: Fist of Fury
497642.description: Bruce Lee stars in this iconic action film about a student who fights for the honor of the oppressed Chinese people and to avenge his master’s murder

507852.title: Above the Shadows
507852.description: A woman who became literally invisible to others after her mother died works as a sleuth until meeting a jaded fighter, the only one who can see her.

512448.title: New Jack City
512448.description: Two streetwise cops embark on the riskiest mission of their careers when they go undercover to bust a ruthless drug kingpin reigning over Harlem.

516859.title: The Last Witch Hunter
516859.description: A fearless, immortal witch hunter ends up in a ferocious battle with supernatural enemies as he fights to save the human race from evil.

520213.title: Train to Busan (Dubbed)
520213.description: A father and his estranged daughter are trapped on a speeding train full of fellow passengers when a zombie virus breaks out in South Korea.

525069.title: The Mountain II
525069.description: After training in a covert special operations squad, two unlikely best friends begin their first mission to rescue an ISIS-captured reporter in Iraq.

527970.title: Blitz
527970.description: A tough cop and his sidekick, who faces ridicule from their homophobic squad, are dispatched to take down a serial killer who targets the police.

528599.title: Takers
528599.description: High-octane thriller about a group of notorious criminals whose streak of untraceable bank heists may come to an end thanks to a hardcore detective.

543161.title: Apocalypto
543161.description: A Mayan warrior braves the treacherous jungle to fight off attacking members of an opposing tribe in order to save his family.

543873.title: Desperado
543873.description: Stunning visuals highlight this action classic as a lone and mysterious gunman shoots through a border town to find his girlfriend’s killer.

545512.title: Blade II
545512.description: Blade, the vampire-human hybrid, joins forces with a highly-skilled team of vampires to vanquish a new race of super vampires out for Armageddon.

550824.title: The Hunger Games
550824.description: In a dystopian future, 16-year-old Katniss volunteers to take her younger sister’s place in a battle where children must fight to stay alive.

550826.title: The Hunger Games: Catching Fire
550826.description: As Katniss and Peeta embark on their victory tour, President Snow plans an even deadlier new Hunger Games, which threatens the future of Panem.

550828.title: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay Part 2
550828.description: The celebrated movie series reaches its epic climax, as the brave Katniss fights to liberate Panem's citizens in a final showdown with President Snow.

551255.title: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay Part 1
551255.description: The franchise phenomenon continues, as Katniss, having survived The Hunger Games, rises with District 13 to battle the oppressive President Snow.

557221.title: Cop Out
557221.description: Bruce Willis and Tracy Morgan star as an oddball pair of NYPD partners who must take on a ruthless, memorabilia-obsessed criminal.

559330.title: Attack the Block
559330.description: A teen gang must defend their neighborhood from savage aliens who turn their apartment complex into an intergalactic warzone.

561851.title: 2Eleven
561851.description: Two brothers and fellow hustlers with very different motivations for committing robberies come to blows the more their criminal enterprise grows.

563036.title: Bad Company
563036.description: When his identical twin brother is killed in the line of duty, a streetwise punk is recruited by a CIA agent to stop an arms deal from going bad.

563040.title: Dead Presidents
563040.description: A Vietnam War veteran returns home and is drawn into a life of crime when he pulls off a daring armored car robbery with a group of fellow vets.

563168.title: Predators
563168.description: A mercenary reluctantly leads a group of elite warriors mysteriously brought together on a jungle planet where they are hunted by an alien race.

565416.title: Damage
565416.description: Ex-con John Brickner joins an underground fighting community to pay for the heart transplant of the daughter of the man he killed.

567010.title: I Spy
567010.description: Two mismatched partners, a pro boxer and a federal spy, must avoid international intrigue and deadly traps in order to get back an expensive jet.

572750.title: The Blackout: Invasion Earth
572750.description: A military crew discovers an outpost of survivors surrounded by corpses, from cars to hospitals, and tries to find out the cause of the mass deaths.

573585.title: Journey 2: The Mysterious Island
573585.description: When a young man receives his grandfather’s distress signal from a remote island, he heads off with his stepfather and a helicopter tour team.

585035.title: Hard Target 2
585035.description: After accidentally killing his friend in a match, an MMA fighter self-exiles in Bangkok where a wealthy man tricks him into being hunted for sport.

589063.title: The Specialist
589063.description: An ex-CIA explosives expert with his own dark past helps a seductive beauty avenge the murder of her parents by a powerful Cuban-American crime boss.

589323.title: Superhero Movie
589323.description: In this hilarious parody of beloved blockbusters, a nerdy teenager is bitten by a radioactive dragonfly, which gives him superhuman abilities.

589375.title: Tango & Cash
589375.description: A pair of rival LAPD cops become unlikely allies when both are framed and imprisoned on drug charges that force them in cahoots to clear their names.

591015.title: Proud Mary
591015.description: Taraji P. Henson stars as a steely hit woman working for a local Mob family who finds a protective instinct for a little boy while out for a kill.

591434.title: Trespass
591434.description: When two firemen discover a map leading to a fortune abandoned in a tenement, they become the targets of a vicious gang, led by a notorious mobster.

595396.description: Tells the story of how Spartan King Leonidas and his soldiers numbering just 300 beat King Xerxes of Persia, with an army of hundreds of thousands.

602292.title: Blade
602292.description: A vampire-human hybrid uses his advanced powers and an arsenal of weapons to do battle with the bloodsucking monsters who threaten the living.

605420.title: Street Fighter
605420.description: Jean-Claude Van Damme leads this box-office smash, adapted from the videogame, about a commando and his street fighters out to stop an evil general.

607952.title: True Lies
607952.description: A deadly and talented spy for the government hides his dangerous day job from his family, but his secret heroics take a toll on his marriage.

609721.title: The Karate Kid
609721.description: Jaden Smith stars in the 2010 reboot of the iconic franchise, this time as a young arrival in China who learns self-defense from a karate master.

610528.title: Blade Trinity
610528.description: An all-star sequel featuring Ryan Reynolds and Jessica Biel as vampire hunters who join Blade to stop a virus from being unleashed on the undead.

611206.title: The 13th Warrior
611206.description: Far from home, an exiled ambassador joins a fierce band of Viking warriors, who are attacked by ferocious creatures that devour every living thing.

616790.title: Metro
616790.description: Eddie Murphy teams with Michael Rapaport and Michael Wincott in this wildly entertaining, action-packed hit! Murphy plays Scott Roper, a fast-talking, wisecracking, on the edge hostage negotiator whose offbeat-but-winning style has made him San Francisco's top mediator! Roper will say...and do... absolutely anything to get his man. But when he comes face-to-face with a psychotic killer who's playing a lethal game of cat and mouse, he's finally met his match! Don't miss the excitement as the always amusing Murphy packs Metro with outrageous action that has critics and audiences cheering!

617284.title: A Low Down Dirty Shame
617284.description: A disgraced LAPD cop-turned private eye teams up with a DEA agent in a search for $20 million in stolen cash and the drug kingpin who ended his career.

619654.title: Ip Man (English Dub)
619654.description: Tells the story of the brutality of the 1939 Japanese occupation of China through the eyes of the Wing Chun grandmaster who rose to fight against it.

619656.title: Ip Man 2 (English Dub)
619656.description: When the Wing Chun grandmaster moves to Hong Kong to open a school for the next generation of fighters, he’s forced to take on a corrupt cabal.

620779.title: Siberia
620779.description: After an American diamond merchant and his lover fall into a bad business deal in Russia, they must evade crossfire between the buyer and Feds.

620882.title: Rogue
620882.description: After an American travel journalist heads to the Australian outback to view ancient landmarks, he encounters a man-eating crocodile.

620886.title: The Road
620886.description: Following an apocalyptic event, a father and son travel through North America’s dangerous terrain in the hopes of reaching the ocean.

621292.title: Black Dog
621292.description: An ex-convict truck driver with makes one last no-questions-asked trip, only to discover that his rig is stocked with assault weapons.

628970.title: Hellboy II: The Golden Army
628970.description: Hellboy and his crew of paranormal outcasts face off with forces of darkness in this imaginative adventure from visionary director Guillermo del Toro.

631012.title: El Último Día (Doblado)
631012.description: Una tormenta apocalíptica amenaza con arrasar todo un país. Se levanta un estado de emergencia mientras estalla el caos.

631544.title: Monsters of Man
631544.description: An illegal U.S. military op goes awry when killer robots are unleashed on heroin producers in Southeast Asia and end up wiping out an entire village.

637106.title: Unknown
637106.description: A man awakens from a coma after a car wreck to find his wife doesn’t recognize him, his identity has been stolen, and hitmen are trying to kill him.

638331.title: Cowboys & Aliens
638331.description: “Iron Man” director Jon Favreau directed this sci-fi Western with Daniel Craig and Harrison Ford squaring off against a massive intergalactic threat.

639274.title: La Ley Del Monte
639274.description: Una pareja de niños juran amarse toda la vida y graban sus nombres en la penca de un maguey, pero los padres de ella están en contra de su relación.

639782.title: Ninja Assassin
639782.description: After a trained ninja leaves behind his former life, he works with a Europol agent to take down the hired killers who taught him everything he knows.

641661.title: ¡El Que No corre... Vuela!
641661.description: Toda clase de abusos y atropellos sufre la India María en la gran ciudad, sin embargo, ella convierte todo problema en risas y alegría.

642930.title: Love Sex & Kung Fu
642930.description: After the little sister of a former soldier is kidnapped, she turns into a killing machine, unleashing her fury on anyone who gets in her way.

644877.title: Rio Lobo
644877.description: A former Union officer teams up with ex-Confederate rebels to find a traitor who caused the death of a close friend and now runs a lawless Texas town.

644879.title: Big Jake
644879.description: When his grandson is kidnapped, the feisty head of his estranged family goes home, supposedly to deliver the ransom, but intending to put up a fight.

645268.title: The Hit List
645268.description: It’s a high-octane race against death when a man meets a hit man in a bar who makes him an offer to kill any five people he wants out of his life.

646030.title: Striking Distance
646030.description: Bruce Willis and Sarah Jessica Parker star in this crime thriller about a demoted homicide cop who works with his partner to find his father’s killer.

646858.title: Postal
646858.description: An average man becomes outraged after being unable to find employment. He teams up with a cult leader to go on a violent spree in an amusement park.

651086.title: Hancock
651086.description: A sarcastic, hard-living, misunderstood superhero, whose antics caused him to fall out of favor with the public, saves someone who might save him.

651094.title: Lake Placid
651094.description: At a serene Maine lake, a 30-foot reptilian eating machine hungers for a fragile paleontologist on her first field assignment and a tasty billionaire.

651120.title: The Tourist
651120.description: An American tourist visiting Italy to mend a broken heart is seduced by a beautiful woman, who ensnares him in an international criminal plot.

652105.title: Lone Rider (Español)
652105.description: Al regresar a su pueblo, un soldado descubre que el corrupto latifundista, mandamás del lugar, quiere adueñarse a las malas del negocio de su familia.

656397.title: True Justice: Blood Alley
656397.description: Kane teams with the CIA in Vancouver to catch the lawyer who struck his precinct, and hopes his capture will lead to the mastermind behind the attack.

657674.title: The Edge
657674.description: A plane crash in the Alaskan wilderness pits two enemies and a billionaire against a blood-thirsty Kodiak bear in a brutal struggle for survival.

661142.title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse
661142.description: The third film in the Twilight franchise. Torn between Edward and Jacob, Bella must also confront a vengeful vampire and a string of grisly murders.

661144.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn: Part 1
661144.description: The fourth film in the Twilight franchise. A marriage, honeymoon and child bring unforeseen and shocking developments for Bella and Edward.

663440.title: Dead Man Down
663440.description: A hitman for a New York crime lord is seduced and blackmailed by a victim seeking retribution who leads him on a violent and cathartic revenge spree.

664924.title: Daylight
664924.description: When an explosion seals off both ends of a commuter tunnel beneath the Hudson River, a former EMS chief risks it all to save the group trapped inside.

665895.title: Corrective Measures
665895.description: As tensions rise among supervillain inmates and corrupt staff, the march toward anarchy begins in the world’s most dangerous maximum-security prison.

667422.title: Pacific Rim
667422.description: With alien invaders rising from the sea, a washed-up former pilot and an untested trainee use massive robots to combat the apocalyptic threat.

672442.title: Dredd
672442.description: The head of Mega City One’s elite police force becomes the city’s last hope when a sex worker-turned-drug dealer aims to take over the city.

673630.title: Daughter of the Wolf
673630.description: After her son gets kidnapped, an ex-military specialist, instead of seeking help, captures one of the kidnappers and uses him to track down her son.

675608.title: Saban's Power Rangers
675608.description: Five ordinary teenagers must team together to become something extraordinary in order to save the world from being obliterated by an alien threat.

676698.title: Mayhem
676698.description: The pent-up rage in an office is unleashed with the spread of a mysterious airborne virus that pits the last two uninfected against their coworkers.

676700.title: Nude Nuns With Big Guns
676700.description: Packing heat and taking no prisoners, a young nun strikes back against the men who made her life a living hell in this outrageous modern cult classic.

678881.title: Paul Blart: Mall Cop
678881.description: When a shopping mall is taken over by a gang of organized crooks, it's up to a mild-mannered security guard to save the day.

680196.title: Dangerous
680196.description: A reformed sociopath travels to a remote island to uncover the truth behind his brother’s mysterious death, but he's met by a band of mercenaries.

682043.title: A Score to Settle
682043.description: With only a short time to live, Frankie Carver is released from prison, vowing to track down every last member of the gang that betrayed him.

683734.title: Predadores (Doblado)
683734.description: Después de heredar una casa en un remoto pueblo húngaro, un joven se ve envuelto en un conflicto brutal con el magnate local al que desafía.

685920.title: Brawl in Cell Block 99
685920.description: After he's fired from his mechanic gig, a hot-tempered ex-boxer enters the drug-running game which lands him in the battleground of a brutal prison.

686278.title: Doom
686278.description: Based on the hit videogame, this adventure begins when a call for help from a research station on Mars sends a team of mercenary Marines into action.

692126.title: True to the Game 2
692126.description: Based on a NY Times Best Seller, this film picks up a year after the first film and follows the lives of the characters affected by Quadir’s murder.

694144.title: Godzilla
694144.description: When a giant monster created by nuclear tests descends upon New York, it's up to the U.S. Army and an odd team of investigators to stop the creature.

694757.title: Dutch
694757.description: An ambitious heroin dealer has his sights set on becoming the East Coast’s most feared drug lord while battling a high-profile court case.

694827.title: Accident
694827.description: A group of teenagers suffers a terrible accident during a joy ride but getting trapped at the bottom of a ravine becomes the least of their worries.

696007.title: Impact
696007.description: During a 10,000-year meteor shower, a rogue asteroid smashes into the moon and causes disastrous electromagnetic anomalies of weightlessness on Earth.

698792.title: Assault on Precinct 13
698792.description: Two men on opposite sides of the law join forces in an epic New Year's Eve battle against an enemy that doesn’t follow the code of cop or criminal.

698796.title: They Live
698796.description: After discovering a secret alien cabal to control the Earth with subliminal messages, one man goes on a crusade to awaken humanity from its spell.

698965.title: The Jackal
698965.description: An engaging suspense thriller about a ruthless assassin hired to eliminate a powerful, high-ranking official in the U.S. government.

699306.title: Salvaje (Doblado)
699306.description: Después de que su camión se avería, cuatro mujeres se encuentran varadas en una gasolinera y se dan cuenta de que es una trampa mortal.

701400.title: Detective Knight: Rogue
701400.description: While chasing bandits from Los Angeles to New York, detective James Knight crashes into his dark past, imperiling his case—and his life.

701770.title: Danger Close
701770.description: Major Harry Smith leads 108 novice soldiers into an impossible battle in Vietnam that challenges their courage to triumph against overwhelming odds.

702534.title: El Cuatrero
702534.description: Con engaños, Álvaro y Mariana roban una camioneta y un caballo al ranchero Lázaro, quien los busca para recuperar sus pertenencias.

702542.title: Emboscada
702542.description: Dos hombres sospechan de un presidente y le tienden una trampa para desenmascararlo ante el pueblo sin sospechar que descubrirán otras verdades.

702666.title: El Pequeño Soldado (Doblado)
702666.description: Esta película está basada en la historia real de Seryozha Aleshkov, un niño de seis años, el héroe más joven de Rusia en la Segunda Guerra Mundial.

702693.title: El Señor De Las Calles (Doblado)
702693.description: Cuando un entrenador se niega a hacer que su luchador tire una cerilla, un notorio gángster cobra la deuda matando a su luchador y secuestrando a su hija.

703989.title: Ne Zha (English Dub)
703989.description: A young boy destined to destroy the world must choose between good and evil to break the shackles of fate and emerge as the hero he’s desperate to be.

705428.title: Yenni Thuniga
705428.description: After his fiancé is accidentally killed in a jewel heist gone wrong, a man seeks revenge on the gang responsible.

707024.title: A Writer's Odyssey (Dubbed)
707024.description: Years after his child is abducted, a man is hired to kill the author of a fantasy novel, but the world of the novel seems to intersect with reality.

707513.title: Big Stan
707513.description: Panicked he’ll be defenseless in prison, a gutless con man sentenced to hard time for fraud gets 11th hour training from a martial arts master.

708103.title: Wire Room
708103.description: During surveillance, a federal agent witnesses a hit squad murder a surveillance target and soon finds himself in their crosshairs.

708254.title: Samson
708254.description: A child born with supernatural strength in 1200 BC grows up to lead his oppressed tribe with great valor against the mighty empire of his day.

711946.title: A-X-L
711946.description: A top-secret killer robotic dog developed for the U.S. military develops a special friendship with Miles and will go to any lengths to protect him.

720951.title: Out for a Kill
720951.description: A professor becomes an unwitting accomplice in a foiled Mexican cocaine deal and must escape prison to prove his innocence and take his revenge.

720957.title: Urban Justice
720957.description: A man with nothing to lose comes face-to-face with his violent past as he seeks revenge against the people responsible for his son's murder.

723254.title: Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World
723254.description: A distinguished young captain of the British Navy leads his crew on a mission to take a French vessel with a reputation for sinking British ships.

723256.title: Red Sparrow
723256.description: A Russian intelligence officer tasked with seducing a CIA agent finds her mission and its objective threatened when they both fall for each other.

725835.title: El Niño Sicario
725835.description: Pedro es abandonado por sus padres en una estación de autobuses de Sinaloa y al cumplir los 15 años se convierte en un sicario sin corazón.

100000001.title: Kubo and the Two Strings
100000001.description: After accidentally summoning an evil spirit, Kubo must recover his fallen samurai father’s mystical weaponry and discover his own magical powers.

100000302.title: Real Steel
100000302.description: In a near future where human boxers have been replaced by robots, a struggling ex-boxer and his estranged son reunite while training a robot fighter.

100000320.title: Taken 2
100000320.description: When retired CIA operative Brian Mills and his wife are taken hostage by a vengeful gang leader, they must rely on their daughter's help to escape.

100000776.title: El Diablo De Culiacán
100000776.description: El Diablo se ha ganado la confianza de un renombrado narcotraficante, pero comete un error imperdonable que lo envía de vuelta al infierno.

100000784.title: Ghostbusters
100000784.description: A trio of failed university parapsychologists cash in on an uptick in New Yorkers’ paranormal complaints by setting up a ghost extermination service.

100000853.title: A Lonely Place to Die
100000853.description: Five climbers in the Scottish Highlands are thrust into a violent fight for their lives when they discover a girl who has been buried alive.

100000864.title: Double Threat
100000864.description: An innocent man on a trip to scatter his brother’s ashes becomes entangled with a woman on the run from the mob after a convenience store shoot-out.

100000946.title: Queen of Kings
100000946.description: Tired of the way she is being treated by the drug lords, dancer Alicia decides to rally her girls to take over the Detroit drug game.

100001240.title: One Shot (Español)
100001240.description: Un francotirador que lucha contra un ejército alienígena debe elegir entre su propia vida y la vida de uno de los mismos seres que quiere matar.

100001316.title: Shark Waters
100001316.description: Miles away from shore, a fishing boat is attacked by great white sharks. Those aboard must fight for their lives to avoid being eaten alive.

100001401.title: No Way Out
100001401.description: Forced to take on a double murder case after the suspect threatens his family, attorney Brian Nelson begins to unravel the facts and learns the case isn’t what it seems.

100001593.title: Shaft
100001593.description: After his friend’s untimely death, cyber security expert John Shaft Jr. teams up with his estranged father to search the city’s criminal underbelly.

100001685.title: Instinto Asesino (Doblado)
100001685.description: Un ex policía tiene la tarea de rastrear y detener a un asesino en serie fugitivo que está empeñado en matar a una mujer y su familia.

100001687.title: Tiburón Terrestre (Doblado)
100001687.description: Un grupo científico que intenta modificar genéticamente un tiburón crea una máquina de matar destructiva que ni siquiera ellos pueden controlar.

100001712.title: Detective Knight: Redemption
100001712.description: In the trilogy’s second film, Detective James Knight deals with mercy and justice on his terms when The Christmas Bomber terrorizes the city.

100001799.title: The Raid
100001799.description: When the government’s Armed Offenders Squad launches a raid in his backyard, a local Māori cop must decide which side he will protect and serve. Based on true events.

100001935.title: The Predator
